OL,5,G1300 Murder She Wrote
OL,6,     FJessica pays a visit to Nashville
OL,7,     Fto catch up with her blues singer
OL,8,     Ffriend, Patti Sue Diamond, but
OL,9,     Fmust investigate who poisoned
OL,10,     FPatti Sue and her husband.
OL,11,G1400 Murder She Wrote
OL,12,     FDennis Stanton investigates when a
OL,13,     Fprominent pianist's wife is
OL,14,     Fmurdered shortly after the
OL,15,     Fpianist's hands are badly burnt.
OL,16,G1500 Murder She Wrote
