OL,5,G0055 Prisoner: Cell Block H
OL,6,     FIn the very first episode of the
OL,7,     Fclassic soap, new prisoners Karen
OL,8,     Fand Lynn are admitted to Wentworth
OL,9,     FDetention Centre, where murderess
OL,10,     Fand "Top Dog" Bea Smith rules the
OL,11,     Froost.
OL,12,G0200 Prisoner: Cell Block H
OL,13,     FThe prisoners hold a farwell party
OL,14,     Ffor Bea and Mum. Meg and Bill are
OL,15,     Fhaving problems with their teenage
OL,16,     Fson Marty. With Bea gone, Franky
OL,17,     Fannounces she is now in charge.
OL,18,G0300 Prisoner: Cell Block H
OL,19,     FWith Franky's hold growing in the
OL,20,     Fprison, temperatures reach boiling
OL,21,     Fpoint in an all-out riot in which
OL,22,     FBill gets stabbed.
